ment.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmvSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4f1548c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"3c5f9d5500f214e0324728a94d23c6c7ad2be6d1","tid":1480361,"uid":262851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1e4a737afdba61904add5359537f54bfd0d45c8","tid":1480361,"uid":270371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"要搵咩人做counter sign?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"總之有BNO既人或拿英國護照既人就得"},{"pid":"7f26bd5c2de6ccc3ed4c390a4ee3c092f725e57e","tid":1480361,"uid":270371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c5f9d5500f214e0324728a94d23c6c7ad2be6d1","tid":1480361,"uid":262851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1e4a737afdba61904add5359537f54bfd0d45c8","tid":1480361,"uid":270371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"要搵咩人做counter sign?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"總之有BNO既人或拿英國護照既人就得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:55:27.000Z","msg":"搵律師搞得5得？定一定要係認識嘅人？"}]}